43
00:05:41,215 --> 00:05:42,425
I'll give you my spot.

44
00:05:42,925 --> 00:05:44,052
That's not it.

45
00:05:49,182 --> 00:05:50,308
If that's not it,

46
00:05:54,062 --> 00:05:54,896
