114
00:10:54,195 --> 00:10:56,364
(I was wondering if Yoon Junghan
might be behind it.)

115
00:10:57,907 --> 00:10:59,519
(Could there be accomplices?)

116
00:11:01,118 --> 00:11:02,953
(There might be a possibility.)

117
00:11:03,493 --> 00:11:06,121
(But it's not something
we can confirm right now.)

118
00:11:18,803 --> 00:11:22,181
(The murderer is you, Gi Haneul.)

119
00:11:24,323 --> 00:11:25,199
(Please...)

120
00:11:30,336 --> 00:11:31,840
Darn it!

121
00:11:52,253 --> 00:11:55,423
(Haneul)

122
00:12:03,712 --> 00:12:05,792
The number you have dialed
is currently switched off.

123
00:12:05,792 --> 00:12:07,287
Please try again after the beep...

124
00:12:21,143 --> 00:12:22,853
(Thinking of)

125
00:12:23,342 --> 00:12:24,260
(our memories,)

126
00:12:24,952 --> 00:12:26,996
(I set out aimlessly.)

127
00:12:28,527 --> 00:12:30,852
(I absolutely won't break up with you.)

128
00:12:48,017 --> 00:12:48,934
(Haneul.)

129
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:51,395
