140
00:14:28,096 --> 00:14:29,889
(Where is Haneul?)

141
00:14:34,748 --> 00:14:35,541
Saebyeok.

142
00:14:36,292 --> 00:14:36,917
Ma'am.

143
00:14:38,127 --> 00:14:39,044
Please tell me.

144
00:14:43,257 --> 00:14:45,050
I don't know where he is either.

145
00:14:46,416 --> 00:14:47,084
He just

146
