170
00:18:00,755 --> 00:18:01,590
That was never

171
00:18:04,667 --> 00:18:05,460
your place anyway.

172
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:10,631
Saebyeok.

173
00:18:13,092 --> 00:18:14,802
Are you really not
going to eat anything?

174
00:18:15,843 --> 00:18:17,678
You'll collapse if you keep this up.

175
00:18:19,014 --> 00:18:20,103
It's been a month already.

176
00:19:03,058 --> 00:19:07,286
(Meanwhile, actor Yeo Saebyeok
is raising fans' expectations)

177
00:19:07,312 --> 00:19:09,565
(with his increasingly
striking appearance on set.)

178
00:19:10,357 --> 00:19:13,027
(Actor Yeo Saebyeok
gets more amazing by the day.)

179
00:19:13,028 --> 00:19:15,696
(We'd love to have him
as a guest sometime!)

180
00:19:22,213 --> 00:19:25,676
Seriously, this isn't just a day or two.
Isn't this too much?

181
00:19:26,367 --> 00:19:27,106
I'm sorry.

182
00:19:27,732 --> 00:19:30,151
Recently, Saebyeok hasn't been well

183
