Pull it tighter over there.

220
00:23:27,776 --> 00:23:28,770
I'm pulling it.

221
00:23:29,114 --> 00:23:30,216
Now, tuck it underneath.

222
00:23:31,445 --> 00:23:32,738
- Did you tuck it underneath?
- Hmm.

223
00:23:32,738 --> 00:23:33,238
I tucked it.

224
00:23:35,752 --> 00:23:37,203
Okay, the blanket.

225
00:23:39,227 --> 00:23:40,289
Hold it.

226
00:23:43,610 --> 00:23:44,278
- Here I go.
- Yeah.

227
00:23:44,556 --> 00:23:46,016
One, two, three.

228
00:23:54,345 --> 00:23:55,137
Done.

229
00:24:03,275 --> 00:24:05,110
Seriously, what are you doing?

230
00:24:52,032 --> 00:24:52,616
I love you.

231
00:24:55,631 --> 00:24:56,465
I love you.

232
00:27:28,256 --> 00:27:29,159
I love you.

233
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:32,155
I love you.

234
00:28:36,965 --> 00:28:37,549
I'm

235
00:28:38,258 --> 00:28:39,426
thinking of quitting acting.

236
00:28:41,376 --> 00:28:41,876
What?

237
00:28:43,488 --> 00:28:43,988
Why?

238
00:28:46,102 --> 00:28:46,936
My future dream.

239
00:28:48,935 --> 00:28:49,728
What is it?

240
00:28:51,938 --> 00:28:52,522
It's a secret.

241
00:28:53,719 --> 00:28:54,553
Ah, what is it?

242
00:28:54,775 --> 00:28:55,567
Tell me.

243
00:29:03,324 --> 00:29:04,909
After I lost my memory,

244
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:06,286
when we came here,

245
00:29:06,995 --> 00:29:08,247
I asked you, remember?

246
00:29:10,178 --> 00:29:11,304
"What is this place?"

247
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:15,302
Did you remember?

248
00:29:17,922 --> 00:29:18,423
Hmm.

249
00:29:21,554 --> 00:29:22,138
Tell me.

250
00:29:42,071 --> 00:29:42,655
Our...

251
00:29:44,491 --> 00:29:45,033
first kiss.

252
00:29:58,881 --> 00:30:00,507
(Hello, I'm an actor, Yeo Saebyeok.)

253
00:30:02,208 --> 00:30:03,972
(Actress Yeo Saebyeok Press Conference)
The time I've lived as an actor

254
00:30:03,973 --> 00:30:06,346
(Will quietly walk a new path)
has been like a beautiful season in my life.

255
00:30:06,679 --> 00:30:10,391
But now, I feel another path
calling me from within.

256
00:30:11,601 --> 00:30:15,730
It feels like it's time to fully live
my own life, not just as a character.

257
00:30:16,606 --> 00:30:19,692
Not as a character in a work,
but as the main character of my own life.

258
00:30:20,134 --> 00:30:23,679
I want to spend my remaining time
more meaningfully.

259
00:30:24,577 --> 00:30:26,745
I sincerely thank everyone

260
00:30:27,142 --> 00:30:28,811
who has stood by me.

261
00:30:30,411 --> 00:30:31,996
I hope you all continue to live

262
00:30:32,288 --> 00:30:34,165
