his final work before retirement,)

273
00:31:17,858 --> 00:31:22,463
(the film "Never Forget Your Enemy",
is scheduled for release this February.)

274
00:31:39,066 --> 00:31:42,820
(And so, may you dispel my darkness)

275
00:31:43,234 --> 00:31:45,945
(and fill it with new light.)

276
00:31:46,195 --> 00:31:46,905
(Just as)

277
00:31:47,447 --> 00:31:48,990
(the dawn always does.)

278
00:32:14,394 --> 00:32:17,984
(You become my new beginning every day.)

279
00:32:41,882 --> 00:32:44,919
♪The more I try to run away♪

280
00:32:45,217 --> 00:32:46,900
♪The clearer it becomes♪

281
00:32:48,502 --> 00:32:51,792
♪Even the word "love"♪

282
00:32:52,088 --> 00:32:53,279
♪Can't convey how I feel♪

283
00:32:55,348 --> 00:32:58,421
♪Watching your shadow moving forward♪

284
00:32:58,650 --> 00:33:00,282
♪Sometimes, I resent you♪

285
00:33:00,282 --> 00:33:02,144
♪But without you,
everything feels strange♪

286
00:33:02,373 --> 00:33:07,443
♪The pain also makes me grow♪

287
00:33:08,890 --> 00:33:10,790
♪There is a lot to say♪

288
00:33:10,790 --> 00:33:12,210
♪Trying to separate us♪

289
00:33:12,523 --> 00:33:15,368
♪Even if I look like a fool♪

290
00:33:15,964 --> 00:33:17,484
♪It doesn't matter♪

291
00:33:17,484 --> 00:33:19,450
♪This is how we are♪

292
00:33:19,450 --> 00:33:22,365
♪Connected to each other♪

293
00:33:22,426 --> 00:33:25,945
♪We are truly strange♪

294
00:33:26,426 --> 00:33:29,477
♪Pushing each other away,
yet embracing again♪

295
00:33:29,477 --> 00:33:31,770
♪Between love and pain♪

296
00:33:31,802 --> 00:33:34,813
♪In some corner♪

297
00:33:34,964 --> 00:33:38,449
♪In the end, we can only be together♪

298
00:33:45,556 --> 00:33:49,388
♪Because that's us♪

299
00:33:52,842 --> 00:33:54,202
♪Even if what we said yesterday♪

300
00:33:54,202 --> 00:33:55,656
♪Remains in the heart♪

301
00:33:55,834 --> 00:33:57,626
♪As time passes♪

302
00:33:57,626 --> 00:33:58,842
♪Maybe I'll laugh about it♪

303
00:33:58,842 --> 00:34:00,922
♪Even those painful memories♪

304
00:34:00,922 --> 00:34:02,042
♪Are also ours♪

305
00:34:02,196 --> 00:34:04,776
♪Seems we can♪

306
00:34:04,776 --> 00:34:06,713
♪Be more understanding♪

307
00:34:07,188 --> 00:34:09,372
♪I clearly told myself♪

308
00:34:10,394 --> 00:34:12,652
♪Never to see you again♪

309
00:34:12,890 --> 00:34:15,599
♪But hearing your voice♪

310
00:34:15,956 --> 00:34:16,986
♪I completely break down♪
